[[File:B1_army_and_landing_craft_on_Naboo.png|thumb|right|300px|[[B1-series battle droid]]s served as the main infantry of the [[Trade Federation Droid Army]] and the [[Separatist Droid Army]].]]
'''Infantry''' was the branch of an [[army]] consisting of [[soldier]]s trained to fight on foot. Infantrymen, colloquially referred to as "'''grunts'''," were also collectively known as '''ground forces'''. In order to survive on the [[Ground warfare|battlefield]], they relied on their training and equipment almost as much as they relied on one another.<ref name="VE">''[[Star Wars: The Visual Encyclopedia]]''</ref> Every member of the [[Resistance]] received infantry training.<ref name="Bomber Command">''[[The Last Jedi: Bomber Command]]''</ref>

